    out ‚Ü© out ‚ąĺ "src_next_household_policy_expense_budget_group_other: " ‚ąĺ (‚ÄĘFmt s.expense_budget_group_other_count) ‚ąĺ (@+10)
    out ‚Ü© out ‚ąĺ "src_next_household_policy_expense_spend_class_variable: " ‚ąĺ (‚ÄĘFmt s.expense_spend_class_variable_count) ‚ąĺ (@+10)
    out ‚Ü© out ‚ąĺ "src_next_household_policy_expense_spend_class_fixed: " ‚ąĺ (‚ÄĘFmt s.expense_spend_class_fixed_count) ‚ąĺ (@+10)
    out ‚Ü© out ‚ąĺ "src_next_household_policy_expense_spend_class_missing: " ‚ąĺ (‚ÄĘFmt s.expense_spend_class_missing_count) ‚ąĺ (@+10)
    out ‚Ü© out ‚ąĺ "src_next_household_policy_expense_spend_class_other: " ‚ąĺ (‚ÄĘFmt s.expense_spend_class_other_count) ‚ąĺ (@+10)
    out ‚Ü© out ‚ąĺ "src_next_household_policy_actual_budget_group_daily_total: " ‚ąĺ (‚ÄĘFmt s.actual_budget_group_daily_total) ‚ąĺ (@+10)
    out ‚Ü© out ‚ąĺ "src_next_household_policy_actual_budget_group_flex_total: " ‚ąĺ (‚ÄĘFmt s.actual_budget_group_flex_total) ‚ąĺ (@+10)
    out ‚Ü© out ‚ąĺ "src_next_household_policy_actual_budget_group_reserve_total: " ‚ąĺ (‚ÄĘFmt s.actual_budget_group_reserve_total) ‚ąĺ (@+10)
    out ‚Ü© out ‚ąĺ "src_next_household_policy_actual_budget_group_missing_total: " ‚ąĺ (‚ÄĘFmt s.actual_budget_group_missing_total) ‚ąĺ (@+10)
    out ‚Ü© out ‚ąĺ "src_next_household_policy_actual_budget_group_other_total: " ‚ąĺ (‚ÄĘFmt s.actual_budget_group_other_total) ‚ąĺ (@+10)
    out ‚Ü© out ‚ąĺ "src_next_household_policy_plan_budget_group_daily_total: " ‚ąĺ (‚ÄĘFmt s.plan_budget_group_daily_total) ‚ąĺ (@+10)
    out ‚Ü© out ‚ąĺ "src_next_household_policy_plan_budget_group_flex_total: " ‚ąĺ (‚ÄĘFmt s.plan_budget_group_flex_total) ‚ąĺ (@+10)
    out ‚Ü© out ‚ąĺ "src_next_household_policy_plan_budget_group_reserve_total: " ‚ąĺ (‚ÄĘFmt s.plan_budget_group_reserve_total) ‚ąĺ (@+10)
    out ‚Ü© out ‚ąĺ "src_next_household_policy_plan_budget_group_missing_total: " ‚ąĺ (‚ÄĘFmt s.plan_budget_group_missing_total) ‚ąĺ (@+10)
    out ‚Ü© out ‚ąĺ "src_next_household_policy_plan_budget_group_other_total: " ‚ąĺ (‚ÄĘFmt s.plan_budget_group_other_total) ‚ąĺ (@+10)
  }‚ćüs.has_policy_metadata @
  out
}

{ BuildSummary ‚áź BuildSummary,
